Description:
    Generate Metronic show view for nested resource (e.g., issues/employees).

Example:
    rails g views:metronic:show issues/employees --namespace=protected
    rails g views:metronic:show issues/employees --namespace=protected --force"

Options:
    --namespace=protected   Namespace for views

Notes:
    - Assumes nested routes exist like:
      protected_employee_issue_path(parent, issue)
      edit_protected_employee_issue_path(parent, issue)
      protected_employee_issues_path(parent)
    - The generator renders a page header with actions and a details partial.